<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to AnoTS</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
        }

        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4285F4;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .user-info {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .custom-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #4285F4;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3367d6;
        }

        .separator {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #ccc;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-message">Welcome to AnoTS!</div>
        <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
        <div class="custom-message">
            <p>Welcome to the AnoTS community. We are very pleased with your participation. Start realizing your dream today.</p>
            <a href="https://nodejs.org"><button class="button"> Get Started</button></a>
            <p>from AnoTS to {{email}}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="separator"></span>
        <p class="signature">Best regards,<br>The AnoTS team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
